At least one human has gotten tuberculosis from a marine animal as noted
in
the following reference.
Thompson, P.J., Cousins, D.V., Gow, G.L., Collins, D.M., Williamson,
B.H.
and Dagnia, H.T., 1993. Seals, seal trainers, and mycobacterial
infection.
American Review of Respiratory Disease, 147:164-167.
